Summary: metallic white clyinder at high altitude moving at high speed no sound
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile on break at work a something caught my eye. I saw a metallic white object moving at high speed at a high altitude moving north to south. Thought it was a commercial jet but it made no sound and I saw no shadows or protrusions indicating wings. Also seemed to increase in speed. Very clear skied and still daylight. Moved from horizon to horizon in 20 seconds or less
